</div>
</div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:322px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Religion_in_the_world.PNG" class="image" title="Map showing relative importance of religion by country. Based on a 2006-2008 worldwide survey by Gallup."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/5/54/Religion_in_the_world.PNG/320px-Religion_in_the_world.PNG" width="320" height="143" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:Religion_in_the_world.PNG" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
